oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: E. T. Wickham "John Wickham on Horseback" statue
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: "John Wickham on Horseback." As a result of exposure to the elements and vandals, the rider's head is missing. Statue circa 1952-1970.
This item is part of Enoch Tanner Wickham's concrete park located near Buck Smith Rd., Palmyra, TN.
